sql_fr_run: with tmp (select max(abs(((cur_cnt-metric)/metric)*100)) as metric from (select count(1) as cur_cnt, brand_nm as product from com_us_lake.dagg_bax_comp cmp join (select src.row_key,src.brand_nm,franchise_nm,src.prod_ndc_id from (SELECT prd_prod_key as row_key,brand_nm,franchise_nm,prod_ndc_id,row_number() over(partition by prod_ndc_id order by prod_id desc) as rn FROM COM_US_HUB.ref_prd_prod WHERE aud_row_stat_ind='0') src where rn=1) pr on cmp.ndc_number = pr.prod_ndc_id where to_date(ship_date,'yyyyMMdd') between trunc(add_months(current_date, -1), 'mm') and date_add(trunc((current_date), 'mm'), -1) and upper(franchise_nm) = 'HEMATOLOGY' group by brand_nm) cur inner join (select prv_count as prv_cnt, metric, sub_field_name as product from com_us_lake.dq_count_table where rule_key = 3211) prv on cur.product=prv.product) select * from tmp
